            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nDuring testing, the \"Set Card\" option appeared in unexpected places (e.g. on successful orders). Before deciding whether to remove or restrict it, the team needs to investigate and document exactly what this function does in the back end, particularly to understand any unintended side effects.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**\n\n* Behaviour of \"Set Card\" function is documented\n* Decision made on whether it should be hidden, restricted, or retained with correct placement\n\n",
