            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nThe logistics section lists supported cities but the colours make it difficult to distinguish supported from unsupported locations. A map (which existed in the previous version) needs to be added back so agents can visually verify delivery support areas for customers.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**\n\n* A map is visible in the logistics section of the back end\n* The map accurately reflects supported delivery areas\n* Agents can verify whether a customer's location is in a supported delivery zone\n\n1. Regions should have a map, and the colour of the regions shoul dbe darker: [https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/logistics/locations/regions](https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/logistics/locations/regions)\n\n",
            "url": "https://silvertree-holdings-dev.atlassian.net/browse/UC-2836",
