            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nWhen an agent attempts to create a refund, the function is broken — it either returns an error message or enters a loading state without completing. This was flagged as a priority item for the next testing session.\n\n**Steps to reproduce**\n\n1. Navigate to an eligible order\n2. Attempt to create a refund\n\n**Expected:** Refund is created successfully\n\n**Actual:** Function throws an error or enters a loading state without completing  \n\n![](blob:https://media.staging.atl-paas.net/?type=file&localId=null&id=76c66c6a-93bc-4962-8aa3-153b3ec029ab&&collection=&height=1032&occurrenceKey=null&width=1920&__contextId=null&__displayType=null&__external=false&__fileMimeType=null&__fileName=null&__fileSize=null&__mediaTraceId=null&url=null)\n",
