            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nPayment options \"Set Card\" and \"Mark as Paid\" are appearing on orders that have already been successfully paid. These options were previously unavailable on successful orders and should only show for failed or pending orders.\n\n**Expected:** \"Set Card\" and \"Mark as Paid\" only appear on failed or pending orders\n\n**Actual:** These options appear on successfully completed orders\n\n![](blob:https://media.staging.atl-paas.net/?type=file&localId=null&id=95928582-91b1-485f-adac-3073204415e9&&collection=&height=1032&occurrenceKey=null&width=1920&__contextId=null&__displayType=null&__external=false&__fileMimeType=null&__fileName=null&__fileSize=null&__mediaTraceId=null&url=null)\n",
