            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nOn orders that have already been cancelled, action buttons such as \"Cancel\" and \"Revise Manual\" remain active and clickable. Clicking them produces error messages. These options should be grayed out or hidden for already-cancelled orders.\n\n**Expected:** Action buttons are unavailable or grayed out on already-cancelled orders\n\n**Actual:** Buttons are active and clicking them results in error messages: [https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/1ffae82e-a741-4db8-8155-d2856497abc1](https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/1ffae82e-a741-4db8-8155-d2856497abc1)  \n\n![](blob:https://media.staging.atl-paas.net/?type=file&localId=null&id=51c1d441-f611-4708-b7e8-1d4aa64b9ff1&&collection=&height=1032&occurrenceKey=null&width=1920&__contextId=null&__displayType=null&__external=false&__fileMimeType=null&__fileName=null&__fileSize=null&__mediaTraceId=null&url=null)\n",
