            "description": "**Identified in:** Admin Upgrade Testing session (26 Mar 2026)\n\n**Description**\n\nWhen a CS agent clicks on an order receipt while in the 'Users' section, they are incorrectly redirected to the 'Sales' section. The agent cannot return to the user page by clicking the customer's name — the only workaround is using the browser back arrow.\n\n**Steps to reproduce**\n\n1. Navigate to the 'Users' section\n2. Open a user's profile\n3. Click on an order receipt\n4. Agent is redirected to the 'Sales' section\n\n**Expected:** Agent remains within the 'Users' section when viewing order details[https://admin.a.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/12c8adfc-5ba1-4670-a9d9-cac9fef43378](https://admin.a.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/12c8adfc-5ba1-4670-a9d9-cac9fef43378)\n\n**Actual:** Agent is taken to 'Sales' section with no easy way back to the user - [https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/12c8adfc-5ba1-4670-a9d9-cac9fef43378](https://admin.c.staging.ucook.co.za/sales/orders/12c8adfc-5ba1-4670-a9d9-cac9fef43378)",
