            "description": "**Background**\n\n* We need to validate the updated transactional mailers end-to-end in a controlled environment before going live. There is a branch that Anand worked on; we need to test the mailers from that branch.\n\n**Detailed Requirements**  \n1\\. Push the latest transactional mailer templates and configuration to staging D.  \n2\\. Ensure all relevant transactional events (e.g., account creation, order confirmation, password reset, billing notifications) are wired to use the updated templates on that branch.  \n3\\. Configure test recipients (internal UCOOK emails) to receive the transactional mailers:  \n[masechaba@ucook.co.za](mailto:masechaba@ucook.co.za)  \n[kirsty@ucook.co.za](mailto:kirsty@ucook.co.za)\n\n[georgiah@silvertreebrands.com](mailto:georgiah@silvertreebrands.com)\n\n**Test Cases**\n\n* All test mailers show correct branding, subject lines, from address, and tracking parameters.\n\n**Notes**\n\n* Scope: transactional emails only (no marketing journeys)\n\n",
