            "description": "**Background**\n\n* Modernize the Web-Admin application by migrating from React 16/Webpack/AntD v3 to React 18/Vite/AntD v5 to improve performance, developer experience, and maintainability.\n\n**Detailed Requirements**\n\n| **Phase** | **Details** |\n| --- | --- |\n| 1 | **Vite Swap** |\n| **2** | **Dependency Cleanup** |\n| **3** | **React 18 & TS 5** |\n| **3.5** | **Tech Debt (Immer)** |\n| **4** | **Apollo Consolidation** |\n| **5** | **AntD v5 UI** |\n\n#### **Risks & Blockers**\n\n* **Runtime Stability:** Potential for uncaught runtime errors in legacy components due to breaking API changes in AntD v5 and React 18.\n* **Visual Regressions:** CSS-in-JS migration may cause minor layout shifts compared to original LESS styles.\n* **Testing:** Need to verify all critical user flows (Login, Dashboard, Forms) manually or via E2E tests as unit tests might be outdated.\n\n‌\n\n**Relevant Links/Images**\n\n* \n\n**Test Cases**\n\n| **Test** | **P/F** | **Notes** |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Font changes  | F | Making a note here that we need to change the font. |\n| Content:  \n\\- Page Sections | Page Section: Create, Delete, Update.   \nImages: Weird spacing in filter section, Create does not work, Delete works, Edit does not work, ![](blob:https://media.staging.atl-paas.net/?type=file&localId=null&id=693416b5-3c18-4020-b21b-326341d402c2&&collection=&height=167&occurrenceKey=null&width=230&__contextId=null&__displayType=null&__external=false&__fileMimeType=null&__fileName=null&__fileSize=null&__mediaTraceId=null&url=null)   \n | Search for page sections?  \nWhy do we need to move them down and up?  \n |\n",
